Package: txnheterogeneity
Title: Calculate transcriptional heterogeneity in bulk RNA-seq, scRNA-seq, and scATAC-seq data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("S", "Sobti", , "sobtisushil@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides functions to calculate and visualize transcriptional heterogeneity across different types of 
    RNA-seq data, including bulk RNA-seq, single-cell RNA-seq (scRNA-seq), and single-cell ATAC-seq (scATAC-seq). 
    It aims to facilitate the analysis of gene expression variability and regulatory element accessibility in heterogeneous cell populations.
